      {
         "id": "SECTION_introduction",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<h3>Introduction</h3><p>This page refrains from depicting specific ancestors due to its focus on prehistory (<htcite0>), which lacks textual records mentioning names. Instead, we delve into scientific studies that enable us to estimate the number of generations since our origin.</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "5390fa3b-735f-4e22-ac98-178303a13fdb",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "The writing system",
                     "date_time": {
