      {
         "id": "SECTION_dispersion",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<h3>Human Migration</h3><p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"originmigration\"  class=\"imgcenter\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('originmigration', '0%')\" /><b>Figure 1</b>: Human migration map <span id=\"OriginHTMW\"></span></p><p>The Figure 1 shows how our specie migrate on the planet. You can expand it clicking on top of the image and return it to original size clicking again.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "Our species emerged somewhere in Africa between 350,000 and 200,000 years ago, according to fossil evidence. However, the migration out of Africa did not happen immediately. Around 70,000 to 50,000 years ago, Homo sapiens began migrating to different regions of Asia. Fossils also indicate another major migration between 45,000 and 35,000 years ago, moving towards the European continent and northeastern Asia (<htcite0>; <htcite1>; <htcite2>; <htcite3>; <htcite4>; <htcite5>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "2be849f1-551b-44eb-8fc6-87027dbf8a68",
                     "text": "Mounier, A., & Mirazón Lahr, M.",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2019",
                        "month": "-1",
                        "day": "-1"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "ed998d95-1afb-4021-9181-2c81d1d9ecd5",
                     "text": "Arango-Isaza, E., et al",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2023",
                        "month": "-1",
                        "day": "-1"
                     }
                  },
                  {
