      {
         "id": "SECTION_genetic",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<h3>Fundamental evolutionary concepts</h3><p>To comprehend the origins of our species, it's imperative to grasp key biological concepts. Through these lenses, we understand that our emergence stems from natural processes of speciation, driven by evolution. The term \"evolution\", applied to Charles Darwin's theory, can be misleading for some readers, implying progress towards a higher state, when in fact, it denotes a series of changes known as mutations (<htcite0>), occurring across generations. These mutations in DNA, when advantageous, enhance the species' adaptability to environmental conditions (<htcite1>), thus increasing their likelihood of being passed down through genetic transmission.</p><p>Given the necessity to track changes over generations, we opt to utilize mitochondrial DNA and the Y chromosome. These uniparental DNA markers, enable a more efficient genetic mapping of distant ancestors compared to autosomal DNA (<htcite2>).</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "6ebf58d7-2f1d-47b6-84ac-07d1430c2981",
                     "text": "DNA and Mutations",
                     "page": "Berkeley",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "12",
                        "day": "22"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "71093c75-b1eb-4289-9711-698b054af418",
                     "text": "National Geographic",
                     "page": "Evolution: Changing Species Over Time",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "01",
                        "day": "24"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "48954556-6e7a-49e0-b844-04c365ad3436",
                     "text": "Jinam, Timothy A., et al.",
                     "page": "pp. 3515",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2012",
                        "month": "12",
                        "day": "05"
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": [
