            {
               "text": "<p>The coexistence of two closely related human species spurred research into their origins. After examining four different models, Phillip Endicott <i>et al.</i> concluded that both species originated during the Middle Pleistocene, approximately 480,000 to 425,000 years ago (<htcite0>).</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "13a06607-7560-4486-9531-9913e2b3ec7b",
                     "text": "Endicott, Phillip, et al.",
                     "page": "",
